27 likes, 0 comments - truefilmfan on November 13, 2021: "Johnny Depp plays Ed Wood the hopelessly untalented but sincerely motivated director of PLAN 9 FROM OUTER SPACE in Tim Burton's affectionate tribute to the world's worst filmmaker in ED WOOD (1994). In wondrous and luminous black and white.  Music by Howard (LORD of the RINGS) Shore.
